      "ALL our jobs are US based and candidates must be in the US with valid US Work Authorization. Please apply on our website directly." Client:


      Istio/DevOps Engineer III Location:


      1100 Louisiana Street, 10th Floor Houston, TX 77002 Schedule


      5 days a week onsite | 7:30am-5pm | Fridays are half days (totaling 40 hrs./week) Term:


      6 Month Contract Rate


      $108-117/hr C2C


      Interview Process


      2 Virtual Interviews (2nd round interview possibly onsite)


      Top Skills


      Strong expertise in Istio and Kubernetes, including hands-on experience with Istio installation, configuration, and troubleshooting is required. Strong expertise in implementing micro-services architecture is required. 2+ years of experience implementing on-premises micro-services architecture is required. 5+ years of experience with CI/CD pipelines and containerization technologies (e.g., Docker, Kubernetes) is required. 5+ years of experience in DevOps or Site Reliability Engineering (SRE) roles is required. In-depth knowledge of networking concepts, including TCP/IP, DNS, and HTTP is required. Security-minded with experience implementing security measures in a micro-services environment is required.


      Additional Notes


      The manager has stated that


      Applicants who do not have documented experience of required skill-sets


      WILL NOT BE CONSIDERED. This team is looking for someone very technically savvy, but also someone who is going to be a good personality fit since they will be in the office 5 days a week with the rest of the team.


      Candidates need to be personable.
